body:
`x = variable.rand_mode` works, however `x=variable.rand_mode()` does not. and gives currently `Unsupported: static cast to 'bit' from 'VOIDDTYPE'`

e.g.

```
class Qux extends Bar;
  rand int y;
  function bit get_rand_mode();
     return bit'(y.rand_mode());
  endfunction
```

